  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6775.63 sitting between the major negative gamma wall at 6765 (-14972.8M) and positive gamma peak at 6780 (+22855.9M), dealers are currently in accumulation mode as they're below the 6786 flip strike in PIN regime. The massive GEX surge (67% 1-min change) indicates heavy options flow just hit, likely creating this tight 15-point gamma sandwich that should contain price action. Dealers will aggressively buy any dip toward 6765 and sell strength into 6780, with 6786 flip strike acting as the key pivot for regime change.\n\nKey levels: 6765 (buy wall), 6780 (sell wall), 6786 (regime flip).\n\n**Bottom line:** Expect tight range-bound trading between 6765-6780 with strong dealer intervention at both levels.",
